This repository contains code necessary to recreate analyses in: 

San Roman, A.K., Godfrey, A.K., Skaletsky, H., Bellot, D.W., Groff, A.F., Harris, H.L., Blanton, L.V., Hughes, J.F., Brown, L., Phou, S., Buscetta, A., Kruszka, P., Banks, N., Dutra, A., Pak, E., Lasutschinkow, P.C., Keen, C., Davis, S.M., Tartaglia, N.R., Samango-Sprouse, C., Muenke, M., and Page, D.C. (2021) Quantitative analysis of gene expression on the inactive human X chromosome. bioRxiv doi: https://doi.org/10.1101/2021.08.09.455676 

Each folder contains code and processed data that may be used to recreate one or more figures and tables:  
Saturation_analysis: Fig. S1
Model_fitting: Fig. S2
Linear_regressions: Fig. 2, 3, S3, Tables S2, S4, S5
Linear_regressions_transcripts: Fig. S5, Table S3
Microarray_comparison: Fig. S4
Allele_specific_expression: Fig. 4, Table S6, Note S1
Gene_constraint: Fig. 5, Tables 2, S7, S8
